title: Thousands of dead starfish wash up on English coast
text:
Thousands of dead starfish wash up on English coast   00:46 
Starfish, lobsters, gulls and fish washed up on a beach in south west England following days of Arctic temperatures across Europe. Rough cut (no reporter narration). ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
